data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nestled in the heart of Lithia, FL, this remarkable property offers a true escape. It’s expansive 5-acre lot and meticulously updated and maintained 3 bedroom home harmoniously combine modern comforts with a serene, self-sufficient lifestyle. With no HOA restrictions, you have the freedom to bring your toys and explore the endless possibilities this haven provides, all while enjoying the utmost privacy, thanks to the gated entrance and fence surrounding the property. Equestrian enthusiasts will find their dream come true with a 6-stall horse/livestock barn, tack and feed rooms, indoor wash area, a spacious arena, and plenty of outdoor space for riding and training. For those looking for the ultimate outdoor relaxation, the pool, complete with an oversized patio and covered seating area, offers cooling swims during the heat of summer and endless opportunities for unforgettable get togethers. Embrace your green thumb with ample room for gardening and don’t miss the chicken coop! Inside, the home exudes an inviting atmosphere, with abundant natural light, open spaces, and a modern kitchen featuring ample cabinets, prep island, and granite countertops. Whether you’re seeking the perfect blend of indoor/outdoor living or a homesteader’s paradise, this home will check all of your boxes.These 5 acres of land on which this home sits are eligible for the greenbelt classification, offering a fantastic opportunity for future property tax savings if you meet the requirements.  However, it's very important to note that eligibility for the Greenbelt tax deduction can vary and may be subject to specific local regulations and criteria. To determine if you qualify and learn more about the potential financial advantages of owning a Greenbelt property, we strongly recommend contacting your local tax authorities or consulting with a tax professional. Don't miss the chance to own a home with this unique tax-saving feature. Don’t miss out on this exceptional opportunity—contact us today to schedule your private tour!
